{"tid":200320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"每日郵報：若美國認為北韓打算核試，將會發動先制攻擊","createTime":"2017-04-14T00:41:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-14T02:26:33.000Z","uid":11598,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6d9244be1774271ac0b7382e89f906b18c0a3c9b","tid":200320,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T00:41:43.000Z","msg":"英國每日郵報 聽下就算，唔好信十足十 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-4410704/US-prepared-launch-strike-against-North-Korea.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-4410704%2FUS-prepared-launch-strike-against-North-Korea.html&d=h%2B9cq0gO3qQVjfypIz7KRG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=c765eb3a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-4410704/US-prepared-launch-strike-against-North-Korea.html</a><br />\n<br />\nThe US is preparing to launch a preemptive missile strike against North Korea, according to intelligence officials after satellite images purportedly show the regime is gearing up to detonate a nuclear bomb.<br />\n<br />\n根據情報官員透露，據稱衛星照片顯示北韓政權正加緊步伐準備核試。美國正準備發動先制導彈攻擊對抗北韓。<br />\n<br />\nThe US fears North Korea will perform a nuclear weapons test to coincide with the national 'Day of the Sun' on Saturday commemorating the birth anniversary of its founding president Kim Il Sung.<br />\n<br />\n美國憂慮北韓會係紀念開國領導人金日成「太陽節」期間發動核試。<br />\n<br />\nIf the US is convinced North Korea will follow through on a test, it can preemptively deploy Tomahawk missiles from two warships parked in the region, according to US intelligence officials who spoke to NBC.<br />\n<br />\n根據 NBC 引述美國情報官員透露若美國確認北韓會進行核試，美軍可以係附近駐紮嘅兩艘軍艦搶先部署戰斧飛彈。<br />\n<br />\nBombers are also being lined up in Guam, and cyber and special operations on the ground may be utilized, the officials said.<br />\n<br />\n另外，轟炸機已經係關島部署好，隨時可以進行特種行動。<br />\n<br />\nBut experts warn a preemptive strike could provoke Kim Jong-un to attack South Korea, with tensions already ratcheting up in the past two days as Pyongyang issued warnings against US military action.<br />\n<br />\n不過專家警告，先制攻擊可能觸動金正恩神經，引致其對南韓發動攻擊。尤其喺過去兩日平壤政府已經對美軍喺附近嘅行動作出警告。"},{"pid":"903d1afc13320a5c9c0fdb77539bdca47877bc70","tid":200320,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T00:42:21.000Z","msg":"鳩譯試下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d61143471a67d48e7bb3367fe06b148c468cb136","tid":200320,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T00:43:34.000Z","msg":"送肥仔去見金日成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5681a999ae4779f351ffb8f7e44c2f307bb7c2c","tid":200320,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T00:45:52.000Z","msg":"快D幫金仔集氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98cd735fac2c1f5dd148a3b9a983b4eca11d7eba","tid":200320,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T00:52:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b8cd5180b856f701c1423032aa46970866d78c9","tid":200320,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T00:56:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c90d8516e84de73f19b8b06a40994def5d457f0","tid":200320,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T00:57:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得個講字肯郁未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n番來就郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e796fa735b5eb1429884cef56bbdc907f85569c","tid":200320,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T01:05:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得個講字肯郁未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj